import React from 'react' import { isAuthenticated } from '../auth' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import { IMG_URL } from '../config' const ConfirmOrder = () => { const navigate = useNavigate() const cartItems = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('cartItems')) const shippingInfo = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('shippingInfo')) const { user } = isAuthenticated() const totalPrice = cartItems.reduce((ac, item) => (ac + item.quantity * item.price), 0) const proceessToPayment=()=>{ const data={ totalPrice } sessionStorage.setItem('orderInfo',JSON.stringify(data)) } return ( <>

Shipping Info

Name: {user.name}
Email: {user.email}
City: {shippingInfo.city}
Phone Number: {shippingInfo.phone}
Country: {shippingInfo.country}
Shipping Address: {shippingInfo.shippingAddress1}, {shippingInfo.shippingAddress2}
Zip: {shippingInfo.zip}

Your Cart Items {cartItems.map((item, i) => ( <>

{item.name}

Rs.{item.price}x{item.quantity}=Rs.{item.price * item.quantity}

))}

Order Summary

SubTotal: {cartItems.reduce((ac, item) => (ac + Number(item.quantity)), 0)} (Units)

TotalPrice: Rs.{totalPrice}

) } export default ConfirmOrder
